|| Video 11 Mongo DB basic understanding ||

-> Sql me table hoti hai usme rows and colums hote hai and mongo DB ke andar collections hoti hai usme fields hoti hai
and rows ko ham bol dete hai documents
-> hame mongo db me inserOne, deleteOne , and aise hi kuch or operations aani chaiye bass
-> use testdb // database create karna
-> db.users.insertOne({name: "Vishal", age: 21}) // database me value insert karna
-> db.users.find() // database se values ko nikal na
-> db.users.updateOne({name:"Vishal"}, {$set:{age:22}}) // data base me update karna
-> db.users.deleteOne({name:"Vishal"}) // database se value delete karna
-> jo bhi answer aata haiusko aham bolte hai document and name , age ye jo key hai isko bolte hai fileds.